I am excited to share this concept with the world, feeding and nurturing the souls of many through music and food.  The menu will feature my original product, ‚ÄúDisco Rolls‚Äù (Collard green egg rolls): a fusion dish that I created using ingredients of the African Diaspora. 
 
I will be using the ‚ÄúCloud Kitchen‚Äù concept.  Cloud Kitchens are centralized licensed commercial food production facilities where  one or two to dozens of restaurants rent space to prepare delivery-optimized menu items.
 
My goal for ‚ÄúDisco Kitchen‚Äù is to create a home like environment that will attract consumers and like-minded people, I believe I can make an honest living in a space created and filled with love, music and food. 
